\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \b \fs36 Description\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Useful for quickly adding ramps between 'nodes'.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Useful for smoothing transitions between CCs that were drawn at low resolution.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This version of the script uses the following presets:\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab The dialog box is skipped, to allow quick one-click execution.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab The lane in which CCs will be inserted (or velocities altered) is the last clicked lane.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab The CC density will follow the MIDI editor's grid.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab The shape of the ramp is linear.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li360 \fi-360 \bullet \tx360\tab Newly inserted CCs will be selected.\par}
